@startuml UC_26_Configure_Community
title UC-26: Configure Community

|User|
start
:(1) Open Community Settings;
:(2) Update description, avatar, banner, and moderation settings;
:(3) Save the changes;

|System|
:(4) Validate ownership or moderator access;
:(5) Update the community record;
:(6) Return the saved settings;

stop
